# === finding-80ebc199-2dd0-4af5-a977-5ac4022f7ae9 ===
<urn:tesserai:twin:finding-80ebc199-2dd0-4af5-a977-5ac4022f7ae9> <http://tesserai.io/ontology/createdAt> "2026-03-26T14:50:48.627863Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> ;
